{
  "stem": "7094.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it's difficult to describe in words what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have-- there were mixture of young, old, children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whenever I was feeding my child, I always felt the child fed in the train where it was crying and blood almost sucking.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- it was tough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were bewildered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We just didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were hoping we're going somewhere better.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you could see they were old, new, children, every-- the younger working people were taken off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But-- but we were-- we were helpless.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People came to the station to glory-- to-- to-- to watch the performance, because it was October, it was sunny day, and enjoying the performance.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "These were people we were neighbors, lived together for so many years together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was another part of the-- the sort of-- the humiliating,",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the attitude of the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably some of them didn't, but some of them enjoyed the performance and came out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were already three days without any food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my aunt suggested as we were passing Lvov-- because part of the family we still had in Lvov, and in [NON-ENGLISH]-- said, you know, we ought to let them know where we are going.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and she suggested that since I have always been the organizer of the family, that I try to get out to notify them where we are going.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This moment is with me all my life, because I just try to analyze how much of it was my self-- instinct for self-preservation, that I wanted to live, and how much it was that I wanted to notify?",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
